         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="1914_AS_RBH_1_00005"/>Herzliche Grüße!</p><p><rs type="place" ref="#pmb995"><hi rend="latintype">Antwerpen</hi></rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><date>2<subst><del rend="overwritten">0</del><add place="inline">1</add></subst>/5 914</date></p><closer>Ihr <signed>Arthur</signed></closer></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="2"><p><handShift scribe="#pmb2173"/>Es ist hier viel wärmer wie in <rs type="place" ref="#pmb43991">Algier</rs>. Wir hatten immer schönes Wetter, immer gute
               Fahrt.</p><closer>Herzlichst<lb/>Ihre <signed>O.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
